{"talk":{"id":7394,"name":"Mindy Scheier: How adaptive clothing empowers people with disabilities","description":"Do you have a favorite T-shirt or pair of jeans that transforms you and makes you feel confident -- makes you feel like you? That's because what you wear can affect your mood, your health and your self-esteem, says fashion designer Mindy Scheier. Inspired by her son, who was born with a degenerative disorder that makes it hard for him to dress himself or wear clothing with buttons or zippers, Scheier set out to make clothing that works for everyone, including the differently abled. Learn more about how she's made fashion history by producing the world's first mainstream adaptive clothing line.","slug":"mindy_scheier_how_adaptive_clothing_empowers_people_with_disabilities","recorded_at":"2017-11-14 00:00:00","published_at":"2018-01-09 15:58:23","updated_at":"2020-09-28 21:44:23","viewed_count":948722,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":473,"name":"TED@Tommy"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/75c771f271ce633f441d501364ab858e98f8d8db_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/75c771f271ce633f441d501364ab858e98f8d8db_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/75c771f271ce633f441d501364ab858e98f8d8db_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/75c771f271ce633f441d501364ab858e98f8d8db_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/4465a529120da4f59419ad215f61e3cde223d631_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MindyScheier_2017S-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":6767492,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MindyScheier_2017S-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":18719181,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"u